# Smashy!
==========

### About
==========
Smashy! is a breakout clone written in Love2D.  I wrote it in a weekend as a submission for Lawless Jam (http://reddit.com/r/lawlessjam).

### Controls
=============
* The mouse controls the paddle and left clicking will fire the ball.
* Escape - Exit/Pause
* Enter - Start/Unpause
* F11 - Toggle Fullscreen

### Credits
============
Included audio track is Obeck - Clazzic, found on http://soundcloud.com.
Included menu audio is unused, but something I wrote a few months back.
The sound effects were made with my mouth and Audacity.



